          <![CDATA[ <p><b>American Energy Efficiency Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires electric utilities and natural gas utilities to meet performance standards for 2021 through 2035 with respect to cumulative electricity savings and cumulative natural gas savings. </p>]]>
